==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: odograph
<hw>o"do*graph</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>"odo`s</grk> way + <ets>-graph</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A
machine for registering the distance traversed by a vehicle or
pedestrian.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A device for recording the length and rapidity of
stride and the number of steps taken by a walker.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>odometer</ent>⟦br⟧
